### ============================================================
### Biblioteca API - Tests con REST Client (VS Code)
### Instala la extensión "REST Client" de Huachao Mao
### ============================================================

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@adminToken = REEMPLAZA_CON_TU_TOKEN_ADMIN
@userToken = REEMPLAZA_CON_TU_TOKEN_USER
@librarianToken = REEMPLAZA_CON_TU_TOKEN_LIBRARIAN

### ============================================================
### AUTH
### ============================================================

### Registrar usuario normal
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "nuevo@test.com",
  "name": "Nuevo Usuario",
  "password": "password123"
}

###

### Registrar admin (para pruebas)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@test.com",
  "name": "Admin Test",
  "password": "admin1234",
  "role": "ADMIN"
}

###

### Registrar bibliotecario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "librarian@test.com",
  "name": "Bibliotecario Test",
  "password": "librarian1234",
  "role": "LIBRARIAN"
}

###

### Login admin
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "admin1234"
}

###

### Login usuario normal
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "lector1@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "user1234"
}

###

### Login bibliotecario
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "biblioteca@biblioteca.com",
  "password": "librarian1234"
}

###

### Perfil propio
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ============================================================
### BOOKS
### ============================================================

### Listar todos los libros
GET {{baseUrl}}/books

###

### Listar con filtros
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?genre=Fiction&available=true&page=1&limit=5

###

### Buscar por título/autor
GET {{baseUrl}}/books?search=orwell

###

### Obtener libro por ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/1

###

### Crear libro (requiere LIBRARIAN o ADMIN)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{librarianToken}}

{
  "isbn": "978-84-376-0494-7",
  "title": "La Casa de los Espíritus",
  "author": "Isabel Allende",
  "genre": "Magic Realism",
  "description": "Una saga familiar que abarca varias generaciones.",
  "publishedYear": 1982,
  "copies": 4
}

###

### Actualizar libro (requiere LIBRARIAN o ADMIN)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/books/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{librarianToken}}

{
  "copies": 10,
  "available": 10,
  "description": "Descripción actualizada del libro."
}

###

### Eliminar libro (solo ADMIN)
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/books/1
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Estadísticas (BONUS - LIBRARIAN/ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### ============================================================
### LOANS
### ============================================================

### Mis préstamos
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

###

### Todos los préstamos (LIBRARIAN/ADMIN)
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/all
Authorization: Bearer {{librarianToken}}

###

### Todos los préstamos activos
GET {{baseUrl}}/loans/all?status=ACTIVE
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

###

### Solicitar préstamo
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "bookId": 1
}

###

### Devolver libro (reemplaza :id con el ID del préstamo)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/loans/1/return
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ============================================================
### REVIEWS
### ============================================================

### Reseñas de un libro (público)
GET {{baseUrl}}/books/1/reviews

###

### Crear reseña (solo si has devuelto el libro)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books/1/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "rating": 5,
  "comment": "Una obra imprescindible. La recomiendo a todos."
}

###

### Eliminar mi reseña
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/reviews/1
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

### ============================================================
### CASOS DE ERROR
### ============================================================

### Error: préstamo sin token
POST {{baseUrl}}/loans
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": 1
}

###

### Error: crear libro sin permisos (usuario normal)
POST {{baseUrl}}/books
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "isbn": "000-test",
  "title": "Test",
  "author": "Test",
  "genre": "Test",
  "publishedYear": 2024,
  "copies": 1
}

###

### Error: reseña sin haber devuelto el libro
POST {{baseUrl}}/books/2/reviews
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{userToken}}

{
  "rating": 4,
  "comment": "Intentando reseñar sin haberlo devuelto"
}
